Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.88,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're back pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to see the Tomoebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's the Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:29.01,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,At Akari-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:30.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.38,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,He came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:35.30,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:37.68,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:47.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,From five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:48.59,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.04,Episode-Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Fifteen: \N The Protector of Smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.38,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,Overall, he seems to be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:30.42,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,Just be mindful of \Nkeeping him hydrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:34.17,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure he gets about \N400cc of water every hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.83,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:40.85,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, the brain surgeon \Nwill be back from the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:42.30,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,so have the surgeon look at him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:45.19,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would it be all right \Nif I tagged along then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:47.53,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,I have some questions for Hikari-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.43,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.65,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Hikari's very tired, \Nhaving just woken up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:56.98,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,so could you hold off on \Ndoing all sorts of tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.10,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:01.95,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I think... there's a lot of catching \Nup that he still has to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.41,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He should be given a little more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.45,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:11.16,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.84,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me a call if \Nthere are any changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:26.08,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,No, we have to let him \Nget some more rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.74,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you've \Njust seen a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.81,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that's surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:49.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're fourteen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same age as me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.33,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention Akari has a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:59.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I knew things like this \Ncould happen during the hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.79,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is there something \Nwrong with your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.18,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:13.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is really bright \Nand it's hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.89,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you were hibernating \Nthat whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.57,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You're just not used to the \Nbrightness of the surface yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.92,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, back to sleep you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.70,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki will probably \Ncome by tomorrow or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu got all big...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,meaning Chisaki probably \Ngot pretty old, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.02,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a nice body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.71,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you excited, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't care about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.13,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.91,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Your cheeks are bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.67,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,He's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:43.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.23,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.62,Main,chisaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:13.66,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki-san doesn't need \Nto go see Hikari-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.90,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she has some test today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.30,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they childhood friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.17,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:24.38,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Chisaki-san's \Ncolder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.40,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.49,Main,driver,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:56.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Kancho! Kancho! Kancho! Kancho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.25,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... What's with all the racket?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:05.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd give him a real \Ntaste of three years of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.89,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Kancho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:09.88,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I gave them a call, but apparently \NChisaki's busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.47,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.22,Main,Itaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.88,Main,Itaru,0000,0000,0000,,If Chisaki-san and Tsumugu-kun \Nwere going to come by,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:20.20,Main,Itaru,0000,0000,0000,,I would take some time \Noff so we could all barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.00,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to do anything \Nout of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.57,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even put a dent \Ninto the loan for this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.95,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the hard work, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.28,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,What's all that about? \NAnd this early in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.45,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, are you Sayama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.29,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hikari. Just like he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.46,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.37,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I've matured quite a bit, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's sort of gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:50.65,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.72,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:56.00,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, Seiki, Akiyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:59.09,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you around, \Nso let's go see all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.98,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hikari's not completely \Nrecovered yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.30,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:03.98,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.58,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two want a ride to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.61,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna make a \Nfew stops first, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:12.93,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.83,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:23.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream,\N so I don't understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.77,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,"Like a dream"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.25,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the line from a chick flick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.89,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.87,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Not a dream like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:33.50,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is something \Nreally weird and different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.77,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So it's more like a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:43.25,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,And then Egawa had \Nbeen getting around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:46.44,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and in high school, he \Nwas going out with Yaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:50.04,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have tried to settle \Nwith someone so close by, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:53.53,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Honjin is working \Nat the government office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.79,Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.79,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.32,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hikari, all right. \NHikari's come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.67,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,How great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.90,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,Since Hikari came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.90,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,that means the other people from the \Nsea will be up soon, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:19.15,Main,guy c,0000,0000,0000,,They should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:22.68,Main,guy c,0000,0000,0000,,Right about now, we'd be able to \Ndrink some great sake with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:23.64,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:27.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's not talk about depressing \Nthings so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.46,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.79,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,We prepared this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.39,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.55,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,It's the flag you waved \Nat the Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:45.54,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,About three years ago, we found \Nit stuck on the bridge pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.13,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun, wave the flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.04,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wave it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:53.71,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That way, no one will get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:57.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kinda sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.92,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.23,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,You just woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.78,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:10.36,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,I just got too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:13.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.38,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,Help him out, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:17.38,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.24,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,You sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:26.00,truck door,truck door,0000,0000,0000,,Always Smiling \N Saya Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.92,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, please \Ntake Hikari home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.12,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.33,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,All right, study hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.80,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. We're already late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.69,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari hadn't changed at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.18,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,and now I'm the same age he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:44.78,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:56.34,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,If Hikari-kun came back \Nup at this point here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:00.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It means that there's a possibility that \Nthe tidal current changes here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.41,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from last \Nmonth's investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:06.24,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,But according to the \Nreflection of the Tomoebi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.59,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Tsumugu, do you have scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.75,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's a pair in Chisaki's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:21.47,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.25,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.10,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.25,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:37.61,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:41.36,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,How'd I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.21,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty bold question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.82,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Have I changed from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.77,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't seen you like that \Nback then, so I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:02.01,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You used to talk about that \Nback then, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.82,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,About changing, or not changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.93,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,all the time back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:12.11,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want anyone to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:17.62,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No. The truth is I didn't \Nwant Hikari to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.70,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:33.25,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... You did change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:43.39,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten much \Nprettier since back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.75,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.24,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.08,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd take a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.74,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.21,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, have you heard from Chisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.96,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.39,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.36,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two days since \NHikari came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:35.62,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I think Hikari might be down because \NChisaki-san hasn't come to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And Tsumugu hasn't \Nbeen by since either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.15,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could you call them, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:43.79,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it's not like I don't \Nunderstand how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.63,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:49.10,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's hurry and finish this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:59.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done! I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.20,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Chisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.56,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,She left to pay Gramps a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.07,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You seem troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.32,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:23.09,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:25.20,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.20,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't Chisaki-san go see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.91,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'd understand, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:36.01,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm as old as Hikari now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.37,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.17,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.54,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have known each other \Na lot longer than we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:45.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,There have to be things that \Nonly those two understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.01,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being left out again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:47.99,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.18,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.78,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.35,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.03,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:40.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I was swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.90,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come see Chisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why do {\i1}I{\i0} have to go see {\i1}her{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.49,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You really haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,For me, it was the day before yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The Ofunehiki was the day \Nbefore yesterday for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:03.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,For me, time hasn't passed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even right now, I'm overwhelmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.63,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari has a kid, and all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:12.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's still summer, \Nthe scenery... Everything's changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:15.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can't just go \Nwaltz in to see Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us were always together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:21.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and if that Chisaki's changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:24.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see any more \Nthings that've changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's exhausting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think about all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.10,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:36.45,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't that his eyes were bothering \Nhim or he was feeling sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:41.23,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And then the guys at the fishery \Ncooperative give me the flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.80,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The one you were waving at the Ofunehiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:50.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka said that if I waved \Nit, no one would get lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So is Manaka, Kaname, Dad, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:03.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are still lost in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:06.72,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,They're just hibernating, \Nso you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.82,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you came back proves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.98,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going down there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.45,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which way you go, \Nyou can't get into Shioshishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.30,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.30,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.01,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Miu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.45,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.36,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Undies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.21,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.07,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:56.53,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I put it all the way down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.09,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.54,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy that Hikari came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:06.19,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So happy that we were \Nnow the same age...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.70,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:11.37,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,that I couldn't even understand \Nsomething as simple as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.58,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari needs a flag, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.38,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,"Flag"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:26.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So lame. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:56.09,Nishiura,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nishiura
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.56,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hika... ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.29,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:03.24,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Ooshi wanted to make sure \Nit could be heard by everyone sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So now it's the 5 o'clock song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone was thinking about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.50,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.22,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:23.14,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All this about changing or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:33.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You were saying the same \Nthing the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.30,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"The other day"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's the other day for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.65,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared that everyone's \Nrelationship would change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:45.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,After I woke up, I really understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:48.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How scary it is for things to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:50.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:57.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved that you \Ndidn't change at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:08.16,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't need to hear \Nthat from you. Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're as violent as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, have you powered up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.11,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:22.07,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:27.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be surprised at \Nall anymore, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.44,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:29.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.41,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.37,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.83,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did it in a hurry, \Nso it's not the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.34,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,but I fixed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hearts. I thought they'd be cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.58,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Kancho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:56.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're butterflies. Butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:21:00.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Putting hearts and butterflies \Non an Ofunehiki flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.95,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy to see Hikari's smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.18,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kancho! Kancho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:13.98,Main,hikari bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They're butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.25,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of things \Nthat I didn't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.09,Main,akira bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.40,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,and a lot of things that \Ncouldn't be reached...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.50,Main,hikari bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:16.96,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Undies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.80,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.49,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,want to protect his smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:41.45,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:44.03,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I-I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:47.88,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki... Did you see Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:49.95,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.08,0:23:32.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakishima, who's repeating this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:34.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Senpai and respect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.74,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to hold your hand \Nso you don't wander off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:41.38,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice! \NThe person you like woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.10,Episode-Title - Copy,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Sixteen: \NThe Whispers of the Faraway Waves
